    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class SensorSimulatorView
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    SensorSimulatorView keeps the GUI of the SensorSimulator. SensorSimulator simulates various sensors. An Android application can connect through TCP/IP with the settings shown to the SensorSimulator to simulate accelerometer, compass, orientation sensor, and thermometer.
    作者:
    Peli, Josip Balic, ilarele
